	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Happy birthday to you!
<br />
<br /><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NES" class="postlink">July 15 is the Famicom's 25th birthday</a>.  I figured a while back that the dev scene needed a little something fresh to commemorate the event.  Admittedly, I kinda one-upped myself with Mandelbrot Set, but whatever.  Enjoy a dose of 8-bit nostalgia anyway.
<br /><a href="http://www.andrew.cmu.edu/~spkelly/portfolio/software/GrayBox.nes" class="postlink">Here's to 25 years of the Gray Screen of Death!</a>

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


